\par \fs20 
\par 
\par The FROG sampling rate is discussed in detail in Kenneth W. DeLong, David N. Fittinghoff, and Rick Trebino, "Practical Issues in Ultrashort-Laser-Pulse Measurement Using Frequency-Resolved Optical Gating," \i IEEE Journ. Quant. Electr\plain\fs20 ., vol. \b 32\plain\fs20 , 1253-1264 (1996).\fs24 
