\fs36\cf1 Reference Field Calibrations\plain\fs24 
\par \pard \fs20 
\par This window is used in \uldb XFROG\plain\fs20 {\v XFROG_Overview} to select the source of reference field.  This window appears after the \uldb test field calibrations\plain\fs20 {\v Test_Calibration_Window} are entered.
